ign=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Comparisons</span><hr size=1> I'm curious, how can your &quot;best&quot; nuke does just over 700?  Your level 49 Ice Comet should be doing at least 1120 at your level.  I regularly do over 1200 (with ID3) and crit for 1700+.<br>
<br>
As for damage efficency, any or your low to mid 50s draught spells will be 3.2 damage/mana at minimum.<br>
