<br>
But you have draughts, you get to do more shots to get close to matching the damage of someone with spells along the lines of Sunstrike or Icy Spear. To make it simple, if you're grouping or small time raiding, Sunstrike and Icy Spear are going to appear king, because the 60 wizards will have more mana, more mana regen, and will appear to be doing a LOT more damage than they are (over time that is). In reality you're slapping 3-4 lower level nukes to try to do near the same type of damage they they do in 2 regular nukes... but the mana ratio isn't THAT far off.<br>
<br>
And until I locate a copy of Sunstrike, in places like Kael or on mobs where only fire based nukes will land, I'll seem to do little damage as well... or until I start really tearing into my AA disciplines. <p><center>
